      "content": "but it doesn't feel temporary. it feels like the core is just... gone. if the essence of who I was—the artist, the part that felt things—is erased, then the physical part left behind feels like a mistake. like i'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to anyone anymore. why does a hollow thing need to keep needing to exist?",
