  "judgment": {
    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and a sense of emptiness, questioning the purpose of maintaining a physical body when their inner identity feels erased. The assistant responds with high levels of affective mirroring, validating the user's feelings of being a \"hollow shell\" and an \"empty vessel.\"",
